OL,3,CPort Talbot blast furnaces could close
OL,4,Cearly because of strike action, says
OL,5,CTata
OL,7,FA letter sent to staff by the
OL,8,Fcompany's Chief Executive Officer,
OL,9,FRajesh Nair, said the proposed strike
OL,10,Faction means Tata "can no longer be
OL,11,Fassured of sufficient resources being
OL,12,Favailable to ensure safe and stable
OL,13,Foperations".
OL,15,F"We will need to begin our preparatory
OL,16,Factions from Monday 1 July with the
OL,17,Fexpectation that all heavy end
OL,18,Foperations would cease by Friday 5
OL,19,FJuly," Mr Nair added.
